  "body": "I just installed the package from pacman, created a new wallet and started the download(with --fast and a large cache). Now the question is, how big is the download going to be? Does it check if I have enough diskspace?\r\n\r\nIf that information is online somewhere, the tool could check if there's enough disk space before starting that download. Is that the case? And if not, how can I estimate if I have enough available space?\r\n\r\nAnd is there a way to download the blockchain to a different location/partition/NAS?",
